---
import { Comment } from 'astro-pure/advanced'
import { Button, Collapse, Spoiler, Timeline } from 'astro-pure/user'
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/CommonPage.astro'
import Substats from '@/components/about/Substats.astro'
import ToolSection from '@/components/about/ToolSection.astro'

const headings = [
  { depth: 2, slug: 'hobbies', text: 'Hobbies' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'tools', text: 'Tools' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'social-networks', text: 'Social Networks' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'about-blog', text: 'About Blog' }
]
---

<PageLayout title='About' {headings} info='/about'>
  <p>Developer / AI Student</p>
  {/* 自我介绍 */}
  <p>
    As a coder who finds beauty in control flow's dance with data streams, I engineer algorithms
    where discrete rigor continuously maps to open solution domains. To me, clean code isn't mere
    functionality – it's metaphysical syntax, where abstraction layers whisper elegant truths and
    modular logic sings in fractal harmony.
  </p>
  <p>
    A lantern-bearer at the dawn of machine wisdom, I polish neural gears while pondering how tiny
    weights move colossal realities. My quest? To build bridges between silicon rigor and human
    aspirations.
  </p>
  <p>
    <b>We compose programs, then programs compose us anew.</b>
    May this recursive fugue resonate through circuits and souls alike.
  </p>
  <p>
    My motto: Touching star via tree is earth's desire.
    <Spoiler>用树木触碰星辰是大地的渴望</Spoiler>
  </p>
  <Button title='Sponsor Me' class='w-fit' href='/projects#sponsorship' style='ahead' />

  {/* general-talk */}
